data.description:
Why pay rent? You can buy this beautiful home for less than most rentals and enjoy spacious rooms and the convenience of downtown Chester living. Many of the big ticket items have been updated and the home is move in ready.  Sit out on the large covered front porch and deck or sunbath on the side deck.  If you appreciate the convenience of a first floor laundry and half bath as well as defined living spaces like a big bright airy Dining room and a large yet cozy living room, then look no further.  The two bedrooms and bath upstairs offer plenty of closet space and room for king sized furniture.  The gas furnace and 50 gallon hot water tank were updated 2 years ago. The roof was replace about 14 years ago.  The carpets in the bedroom and living room are new!  Just move in and start living. :-)

Now is your second chance to go after this great starter home.  The buyer was injured on his job and had to back out of the contract.  Call right away and see this lovely home.
